ygData.messageBody:
> It annoys me greatly the number of
> people that just sit in the bank at
> Freeport doing absolutely nothing
> but taking up space.
>
> They are probably in groups and talking.
> I do not experience much lag there, so
> others may not be experiencing your
> problem.

Aye, or waiting for someone to buy or sell
something or just waiting to meet someone.
That's fine and well. Wait outside. The bank
is only so big, and it's nice to be able to
get in and use it. I don't so much mind
walking over 50 bodies sitting or standing
around outside the bank if I can actually get
through the door and then to the teller to use
it.
